4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to help individuals become cybersecurity specialists without prior knowledge. The program provides a robust foundation in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration while teaching crucial skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. The bootcamp spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate that is widely recognized. The course is available in English and Spanish, with no previous experience required. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop